VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (@require_http_methods\s*\(\s*\["(?:GET|PUT|DELETE|.*?)"\]\))|(@require_GET)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:@login_required|@permission_required|validate|sanitize
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of insecure or commonly abused HTTP decorators.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for HTTP Decorators: Insecure or Commonly Abused Methods.
